      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "By letter dated March 21, 1960, Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "[REDACTED] N. W.,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Washington, D. C., referred this Bureau to an article",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "appearing in the \"Detroit Times,\" issue of March 9, 1960,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "a copy of which is enclosed, and requested to be advised",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "whether there had been any change in our policy with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "respect to unidentified flying objects; whether this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Bureau gathered evidence of unidentified flying objects for the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Department of the Air Force; and whether the photograph",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "described in the article had been analyzed at FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Laboratories or for FBI purposes. This Bureau's letter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "to the afore-mentioned organization of September 26, 1958,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "had pointed out that we do not investigate incidents",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "involving unidentified flying objects but furnished data",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "received concerning them to the Department of the Air Force.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
